title: Week 9 - Intern Tout Tryouts Round 1
description:
Big Cat, lightswitch Lou and Hank interview 10 potential pick em interns. Each contestant came up with a nickname for themselves and submit their favorite 3 games of the weekend to the boys. We also have Matts 5 team parlay of the week and locks of the weekend!
